Package: koet
Version: 1.18.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8) | python3.9 | python3.11 | python3.12, python3-venv, fping, psmisc, iproute2
Recommends: python3-pip, gcc
Maintainer: cdmaestas <cdmaestas@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/cdmaestas/SpectrumScale_NETWORK_READINESS
Description: IBM Storage Scale Network Readiness Tool with Web UI
 KOET (Keep On Executing Tests) validates IBM Storage Scale network readiness
 by running fping latency tests and nsdperf throughput tests across cluster
 nodes, then comparing results against IBM KPIs.
 .
 Includes a web UI (koet-ui) for browser-based test configuration, live
 streaming output, and Chart.js results visualization.
 .
 Start with: koet-ui  (then open http://127.0.0.1:5002)
 Or via SSH tunnel: ssh -L 5002:127.0.0.1:5002 root@this-node
